text: S.F.’s building department has a 58-page guide called “Getting a City Permit.” It reads: “Obtaining a city permit can undoubtedly be one of the most confusing processes you may ever experience.” That’s the truth, @hknightsf writes. https://t.co/ibRFpM0PoI

text: As officials prepare to distribute the first precious vials of coronavirus vaccine, Bay Area businesses large and small are weighing whether to require or just encourage workers to get it, when their turn comes. https://t.co/eMyUbfT7YS
